<item>
            <title>[LU-9654] fix problem of Remove Archive on Last Unlink policy</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9654</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mdt_handle_last_unlink() calls mdt_attr_get_complex() to get invalid attributes. However, mdt_attr_get_complex() clearups all known attributes. So, the known attribute of HSM or nlink should be checked before calling that function.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
